entity.ad_astra.lunarian.description: What seems to be a villager, evolved to live on the lunar surface. Or vice versa..?

entity.ad_astra.martian_raptor.descripti: Will lunge at you quite violently. A jumper.
entity.ad_astra.pygro.description: Some sort of venusian piglin- did it come from the nether, or the other way around?
entity.ad_astra.pygro_brute.description: Some sort of venusian piglin, with a nasty punch at that.
entity.ad_astra.star_crawler.description: A clump of lichen-esque appendages- almost like a tardigrade.
entity.ad_astra.sulfur_creeper.descripti: It destroys block upon explosion- venusian combustor.

entity.ad_astra.tier_3_rocket.descriptio: The best venusian engineering can offer.
